### Controller — Monitoring Capaian JPL

#### [NEW] [MonitoringJplController.php](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/RSCM/laravel/sipelatih/sipelatih-app/app/Http/Controllers/MonitoringJplController.php)

Endpoint yang akan dibuat:

**1. `GET /api/monitoring-jpl`** — Data ringkasan JPL semua pegawai

Query parameters:
- `search_nip` — Filter berdasarkan NIP
- `search_name` — Filter berdasarkan nama peserta
- `per_page` — Jumlah data per halaman (default 10)

Response (paginated):
```json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Nina Persik",
      "employee_id": "111164826554882134",
      "work_unit": "TK Diklat",
      "scope": "Teknis",
      "employment_type": "Administrasi",
      "position": "Non Kes",
      "jpl_target": 24,
      "jpl_achieved": 50,
      "status": "Tercapai"
    }
  ],
  "meta": { ... }
}
```

Logic:
- Query `users` dengan relasi [workUnit](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/RSCM/laravel/sipelatih/sipelatih-app/app/Models/User/User.php#35-39), [position](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/RSCM/laravel/sipelatih/sipelatih-app/app/Models/User/User.php#40-44), [employmentType](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/RSCM/laravel/sipelatih/sipelatih-app/app/Models/User/User.php#45-49), [profession](file:///c:/Users/qkiki/Documents/RSCM/laravel/sipelatih/sipelatih-app/app/Models/User/User.php#50-54)
- Hitung `jpl_achieved` = SUM dari `activity_participants.jpl_score` per user
- `jpl_target` diambil dari `professions.jpl_target`
- `status` = "Tercapai" jika `jpl_achieved >= jpl_target`, "Belum Tercapai" jika belum

**2. `GET /api/monitoring-jpl/{userId}/activities`** — Detail kegiatan yang diikuti pegawai

Query parameters:
- `per_page` — Jumlah data per halaman (default 10)

Response (paginated):
```json
{
  "user": {
    "name": "Nina Persik",
    "employee_id": "111164826554882134",
    "work_unit": "TK Diklat"
  },
  "data": [
    {
      "activity_name": "Rapat/Rkat BMD",
      "activity_date": "1-10 Desember 2025",
      "scope": "Teknis",
      "employment_type": "Administrasi",
      "position": "Non Kes",
      "jpl_target": 24,
      "jpl_score": 50,
      "status": "Tercapai"
    }
  ]
}
```

